FT  22 DEC 94 / UK Company News: Shares fall 9p at Brit Thornton
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The profits warnings made by British Thornton Holdings in October was borne
out yesterday when the packaging and specialist furniture group reported a
decline in interim pre-tax profits to Pounds 304,000.
