<HEADLINE>
FT  22 DEC 94 / People: Non-executive directors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Marthinus Prinsloo at VEKTRA CORPORATION; Robert Crockett has resigned.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Vektra Corp.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
