FT  22 DEC 94 / Stagecoach deal referred to MMC
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Stagecoach, the private bus operator, has been referred to the Monopolies
and Mergers Commission for its purchase of a 20 per cent stake in SB
Holdings, the former municipal bus operator in Stratchclyde which remains
